{"tid":916913,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實李卓人真係好撚慘，大家唔好再笑佢了","createTime":"2018-11-26T04:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T01:15:17.000Z","uid":29006,"like":46,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5388d715382f59d52b35343e5790d9cc1b1663a6","tid":916913,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:33:41.000Z","msg":"認真一諗 一班泛民 <br />\n急就告撚左啦年年大大聲<br />\n候選人又係咁換<br />\n最後咪又係仲用緊「民主最後希望」做宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舖舖怨天尤人<br />\n睇都睇到嘔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好話泛民死忠次次J啲低質拉票宣傳 <br />\n我連一個Post 都totally no mood to 睇<br />\n最撚慘係乜<br />\n就係根本無野好賴<br />\n下下比人鐵票壓制 又無得賴人搵後生大波妹呃票 又無得賴人金錢式宣傳<br />\n唯有串下馮檢基啦<br />\n哈 屌你老母馮檢基啲票同你李卓人加埋都唔夠陳凱欣多啦<br />\n連唯一精神支柱都冇埋 最多咪又酸又嬲咁話下<br />\n哈 你班香港人無咗我  惡法就會過晒架啦 <br />\n「無泛民撐住  共產黨會整死香港喎」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慘撚到呢個地步 簡直就好似清未班柒頭<br />\n比人打撚到鴉片支煙槍都比人搶撚埋<br />\n又嬲又酸又周身唔唔聚財咁<br />\n成9日FF埋d所謂地區直選否決權 范、曾時代啲泛民議政風氣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陰9公囉"},{"pid":"1463950bdb025a7c47ab5b0c9f15dbf54fd7aeb4","tid":916913,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:40:50.000Z","msg":"嚟嚟去去口號又喺個幾味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話為香港好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鳩up佢地最叻"},{"pid":"ea852e6a9d3b5a60a3cd18f963244e83431fe6fb","tid":916913,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb01c1fda8caa9fe02c15a10d8e55dcc96fa8314","tid":916913,"uid":25601,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:44:43.000Z","msg":"你點夠建制d人玩呀 老人院d老野一車車咁送去投票 仲有d死人都投到票<br />\n<br />\n未投既人都被人投左票"},{"pid":"fcc0ec271b89e8110b98cb5525e8fd48210b0fe6","tid":916913,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1463950bdb025a7c47ab5b0c9f15dbf54fd7aeb4","tid":916913,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:40:50.000Z","msg":"嚟嚟去去口號又喺個幾味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話為香港好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鳩up佢地最叻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T05:11:39.000Z","msg":"睇到悶，從不反省，賴天賴地泛民最叻"},{"pid":"b6d1e63a514491bcbce7a5fa98d1fb6724eecdd4","tid":916913,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T05:57:22.000Z","msg":"我已經開始戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81574e297a25cbae953e747a08d7bd4393db8b1e","tid":916913,"uid":16925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:22:22.000Z","msg":"全因為小麗老師玩讀誓詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecdf695e8993a87809d15dbb5bbe2b63d8af1f00","tid":916913,"uid":29006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b6d1e63a514491bcbce7a5fa98d1fb6724eecdd4","tid":916913,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T05:57:22.000Z","msg":"我已經開始戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:15:13.000Z","msg":"巴打，我地一齊努力"},{"pid":"98a9481a28b805499e956d847768ca035d44f929","tid":916913,"uid":3549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"81574e297a25cbae953e747a08d7bd4393db8b1e","tid":916913,"uid":16925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:22:22.000Z","msg":"全因為小麗老師玩讀誓詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:33:22.000Z","msg":"其實小麗先係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6035365b88dc6252de6c00d3a2dd03e335e9bb1","tid":916913,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:42:06.000Z","msg":"十皮月薪嘅作用就係呢樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁洗鬼投李卓人咩<br />\n投比獨立候選人仲好啦"},{"pid":"aa4397b47ec9cc8d43bb4b696c2ecae026259a97","tid":916913,"uid":29006,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d6035365b88dc6252de6c00d3a2dd03e335e9bb1","tid":916913,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:42:06.000Z","msg":"十皮月薪嘅作用就係呢樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁洗鬼投李卓人咩<br />\n投比獨立候選人仲好啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:56:46.000Z","msg":"係，我都唔明。<br />\n選到你入去，一係唔投票，一係投同建制一樣嘅票(楊岳橋/涂謹申係最好例子)，咁選民點解要選你泛民入去賣港?<br />\n你話，多一把對抗建制嘅聲音，Sorry，其實Facebook, 網台都做到，點解之前又唔見你李卓人做? 選舉近了先開始整色整水?"},{"pid":"97d8463c6d59786018149cbeb22e4817c97b5841","tid":916913,"uid":191338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T08:00:31.000Z","msg":"香港好多所謂區議員/立法會議員都係選前先蒲頭<br />\n選完4年穩袋幾百萬，係某啲敏感時刻搏見報講幾句，其實真係幾好搵"},{"pid":"eb64da865b2bc287dd79e9fd8ab3d897149a72de","tid":916913,"uid":29006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"97d8463c6d59786018149cbeb22e4817c97b5841","tid":916913,"uid":191338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T08:00:31.000Z","msg":"香港好多所謂區議員/立法會議員都係選前先蒲頭<br />\n選完4年穩袋幾百萬，係某啲敏感時刻搏見報講幾句，其實真係幾好搵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:06:46.000Z","msg":"又有好多人忽然留意政治，忽然叫人投泛民。<br />\n問佢地泛民有咩值得支持嘅地方，佢地永遠淨係執人口水尾，話咩香港要贏，建制派就要輸。好多人心中淨係想建制輸就投泛民，從來唔會睇泛民政績同政綱，亦都唔會核對吓泛民喺咁多年有無兌現過選舉承諾。人云亦云，問多兩句呢啲人就會起鋼發你老脾。"},{"pid":"5637f2b1565bc65581b35cd65d8ef4fc1cc285eb","tid":916913,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:20:30.000Z","msg":"悔過書真係好柒"},{"pid":"150738f7b42482f934edac958edefd0aafd55ab9","tid":916913,"uid":39437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:38:20.000Z","msg":"而家入到去有用咩？<br />\n慢慢含啦on9仔"},{"pid":"06ee988637198d136dd586836fabec36d83dc1d4","tid":916913,"uid":209120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:47:35.000Z","msg":"其實阿人係咪比快必累到輸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680593fdb8453bfaa117c53b25835494783e6c28","tid":916913,"uid":28181,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/182351_412dcecd7d84d0a8fcda56880efeafd9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F182351_412dcecd7d84d0a8fcda56880efeafd9.gif&h=5b0e1240&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d12e04ba279db571b385d6f4413b8a62e602e9c","tid":916913,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06ee988637198d136dd586836fabec36d83dc1d4","tid":916913,"uid":209120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:47:35.000Z","msg":"其實阿人係咪比快必累到輸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T01:11:40.000Z","msg":"泛民班友一直自詡係議會入面醒個派，認為建制種無腦係會襯托出自己嘅優秀，但今次為九萬六真係洋相盡出，醜到選民都無眼睇。"},{"pid":"d61e1661e7cafea770db4cbbcb2a2750f4d6a756","tid":916913,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"680593fdb8453bfaa117c53b25835494783e6c28","tid":916913,"uid":28181,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/182351_412dcecd7d84d0a8fcda56880efeafd9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F182351_412dcecd7d84d0a8fcda56880efeafd9.gif&h=5b0e1240&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T01:14:00.000Z","msg":"屌 真係好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c04e973441791a085123a948880c6e900d6529","tid":916913,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T